text: Le Fresne-sur-Loire used to be a commune. It was in Pays de la Loire in the Maine-et-Loire department in western France. Before 1 January 2016, it was part of the Loire-Atlantique department.Décret n° 2015-1751 23 December 2015 On 1 January 2016, it became part of the new commune, Ingrandes-Le Fresne sur Loire.Arrêté préfectoral 31 December 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in Loire-Atlantique
title: Le Fresne-sur-Loire
